<a data-tip="p$t$zhou-quan-43-90" href="/people/zhou-quan-43-90">周全</a>，<strong title="笔棍/游戏文案/懒蛋/屎尿屁专精" class="zu-question-my-bio">笔棍/游戏文案/懒蛋/屎尿屁专精</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhou-zhe-18-7" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhou-zhe-18-7" class="zg-link" title="周喆">周喆</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-xiao-miao-37" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-xiao-miao-37" class="zg-link" title="张小喵">张小喵</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
